    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Imperante domno nostro <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Lodovicus</persName> magno <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs>, anno imperi suis hoctavodecimo, de
                        mense iulio, indicione prima. Livel..32.. <persName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Abbots" ref="#people/1241"
                            >Vvarnefrit</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abes</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monasteri</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Abbots #Rent_in_kind #Operae #Exenia #Actionarii/actores #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47">Sancti Selvestri</orgName> sito <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15">Nonantola</placeName> tibi vero
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers #Freedman"><name ref="Ardebertus"
                                >Ardevertus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Bertus"
                                >Berto</name></persName> vocatur <rs key="#Freedman">livero
                            homine</rs> cum trado tibi vel ad tuis heredis <rs
                            key="#Agricultural_workers">ad lavorandum et supersedendum</rs>. Idest
                            <rs key="#Petiae">sorte</rs> illa qui est posita prope <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvio</rs> Pado in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Actionarii/actores #Operae #Exenia #Wine #Rivers #Rent_in_kind #Linen #Minores #Legumes #Maiores"
                            ref="#places/2492">Ustilia</placeName> et ipsa sorte qui per Bertoni
                        rectam fuit in integrum. Ipsa sorte cum trado tibi vel ad tuis heredis ad
                        lavorandum et supersedendum sine fraudo vel nelicto, livellario nomine,
                        usque ad annis nomero XX et nove. Et <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">reditum</rs>
                        exinde persolvere promito de ipsis rebus de omnem laborem que ibidem Dominus
                        dederit: de <rs key="#Maiores">maiorimen</rs> in canpo cove quarta promito,
                        de <rs key="#Legumes">legumen</rs> in area modio quarto, <rs key="#Minores"
                            >minudo</rs> in area modio quinto, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> scuva
                        quarta, et si <rs key="#Wine">vitis</rs> posueritis retdat vino quarto ad
                        isto omnia <rs key="#Actionarii/actores">misso domnico</rs> supersadstante.
                            <rs key="#Exenia">Etsenio</rs> vero per omni anno dinarios duodecim et
                        ipsos dinarios siad dati et conpleti sit in missa sancti Martini per omni
                        anno. <rs key="#Operae">Operas</rs> sex manibiles et ipsas operas facere
                        deveas ihc in suprascripta Ustilia cum anona domnica; et per tempore megis
                        dare deveas ad misso qui supervenerit nomina vel..4..ldo in ..7..nno quando
                        ipso reditum fecerit et postea dare deveas ..8.. colonus ad misso domnico,
                        sic tamen ut ipso redito colonus cum suo dispengio tragere et dare ..2..
                        ..4..m..1..eas..2.. et vegere deveas ad <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/1538" key="#Actionarii/actores #Houses"><orgName
                                ref="#juridical_persons/1106"
                                key="#Rent_in_kind #Actionarii/actores #Houses">Sancti
                                Marii</orgName> in Borana</placeName> et consigni ad domnico misso.
                        Et ad expletis annis exiad colonus vel eius heredis de super ispis rebus cum
                        tres porcionis de sua movilia ..2.. extra casas, tectoras et curtis clausura
                        quarta porcionem dimitat in ipso cispide nam alias nulla. Ego patrono nec
                        mei suscipsores te suprascripto colonus nec ad tuis heredis nulla
                        superponamus nisi qualiter superius scriptum est. Pena vero inter nobis
                        stetit qui non conpleverit vel permanserit in ea omnia qualiter superius
                        legitur, et certe aparuerit veritas tunc conponat pars partis ubi culpa
                        respeserit ad illa parte qui in suam fidem permanserit pena nomine solidos
                        XX et nove. Duos livellos uno tinore scriptus ad omnia suprascripta. Actum
                        feliciter.</ab>
